The paper presents a math-aware Question Answering System, which involves natural language processing, machine learning, and information retrieval techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Cybernetics (cs.CY).
